title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The first few steps may be the hardest part of your creative process today. Youre not prepared to head off into the unknown, even if everything is in order and ready to go. Youre inclined to chat about external factors that stall you, such as blaming bureaucratic red tape for your delay. However, its your own mixed feelings that most likely sap your confidence. You might feel simultaneously cocksure about what needs to happen and unclear whether youre the person for the job. The time for hesitation is over. Enlist the aid of your muse and trust yourself to rise to the occasion. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
